chanan|[[Inauguration of James Buchanan]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|tanneyf|Roger B. Taney<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n|{{dts|1861|03|04}}<br />(Monday) || Public || {{sort|lincolna|[[First inauguration of Abraham Lincoln]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol ||{{sort|tanneyg|Roger B. Taney<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1865|03|04}}<br />(Saturday) || Public || {{sort|lincolnb|[[Second inauguration of Abraham Lincoln]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|chasea|[[Salmon P. Chase]]<br />Chief Justice of the United States}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1865|04|15}}<br />(Saturday) || Private || {{sort|johnsona|[[Inauguration of Andrew Johnson]]}} || Kirkwood House Hotel,<br />Washington, D.C. || {{sort|chaseb|Salmon P. Chase<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1869|03|04}}<br />(Thursday) || Public || {{sort|granta|[[First inauguration of Ulysses S. Grant]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|chasec|Salmon P. Chase<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1873|03|04}}<br />(Tuesday) || Public || {{sort|grantb|[[Second inauguration of Ulysses S. Grant]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|chased|Salmon P. Chase<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n|{{dts|1877|03|03}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/nr/travel/presidents/hayes_spiegel_grove.html|title=Spiegel Grove: Rutherford B. Hayes Presidential Center|publisher=National Park Service, U.S. Department of the Interior|accessdate=February 5, 2017}}</ref>{{efn|name=4thSunday}}<br />(Saturday) || Private || rowspan=2| {{sort|hayes|[[Inauguration of Rutherford B. Hayes]]}} || [[Red Room (White House)|Red Room]],<br />[[White House]] ||rowspan=2| {{sort|waitea|[[Morrison Waite]]<br />Chief Justice of the United States}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1877|03|05}}{{efn|name=4thSunday}}<br />(Monday) || Public || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol\n|-\n| {{dts|1881|03|04}}<br />(Friday) || Public || {{sort|garfield|[[Inauguration of James A. Garfield]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|waiteb|Morrison Waite<