warrend|Earl Warren<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1973|01|20}}<br />(Saturday) || Public || {{sort|nixonb|[[Second inauguration of Richard Nixon]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|burgera|[[Warren Burger]]<br />Chief Justice of the United States}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1974|08|09}}<br />(Friday) || Public || {{sort|ford|[[Inauguration of Gerald Ford]]}} || [[East Room]],<br />White House || {{sort|burgerb|Warren Burger<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1977|01|20}}<br />(Thursday) || Public || {{sort|carter|[[Inauguration of Jimmy Carter]]}} || East Portico,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|burgerc|Warren Burger<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1981|01|20}}<br />(Tuesday) || Public || {{sort|reagana|[[First inauguration of Ronald Reagan]]}} || West Front,<br />U.S. Capitol ||{{sort|burgerd|Warren Burger<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n|{{dts|1985|01|20}}<br />(Sunday) || Private ||rowspan=2|{{sort|reaganb|[[Second inauguration of Ronald Reagan]]}} || [[Entrance Hall]],<br />White House || rowspan=2|{{sort|burgere|Warren Burger<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1985|01|21}}{{efn|name=20thSunday}}<br />(Monday) || Public || [[United States Capitol rotunda|Rotunda]],<br />U.S. Capitol\n|-\n| {{dts|1989|01|20}}<br />(Friday) || Public || {{sort|bushh|[[Inauguration of George H. W. Bush]]}} || West Front,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|rehnquista|[[William Rehnquist]]<br />Chief Justice of the United States}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1993|01|20}}<br />(Wednesday) || Public || {{sort|clintona|[[First inauguration of Bill Clinton]]}} || West Front,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|rehnquistb|William Rehnquist<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|1997|01|20}}<br />(Monday) || Public || {{sort|clintonb|[[Second inauguration of Bill Clinton]]}} || West Front,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|rehnquistc|William Rehnquist<br />Chief Justice}}\n|-\n| {{dts|2001|01|20}}<br />(Saturday) || Public || {{sort|bushwa|[[First inauguration of George W. Bush]]}} || West Front,<br />U.S. Capitol || {{sort|rehnquistd|