Mines and Technology|isbn=|location=|language=en|ref={{harvid|South African School of Mines and Technology|1910}}}}\n*{{cite book|title=Fatal Avenue: A Traveller's History of the Battlefields of Northern France and Flanders, 1346\u20131945|last=Holmes|first=Richard|publisher=Jonathan Cape|year=1992|isbn=1844139387|location=|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book |ref =harv | title= The Unending Vigil: The History of the Commonwealth War Graves Commission |last=Longworth |first=Philip |year=2003 |origyear=1st. pub. CWGC:1967 |edition=1985 revised |publisher=Pen and Sword |isbn=1-84415-004-6 }}\n*{{Cite book|url=http://archive.org/details/educationinsouth00egma|title=Education in South Africa (1652\u20131922)|last=Malherbe|first=Ernst Gideon|date=1925|publisher=Juta|others=Library Services University of Pretoria|isbn=|location=|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite book|last=Messenger|first=Charles|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=a2OzBgAAQBAJ&pg=PT244|title=Call to Arms: The British Army 1914-18|date=30 April 2015|publisher=Orion Publishing Group|isbn=978-1-78022-759-7|location=|pages=244|language=en|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Miles|first=Stephen|url=https://books.google.com/?id=CTiwDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA51&lpg=PA51&dq=%22perpetuity+of+sepulture%22#v=onepage|title=The Western Front: Landscape, Tourism and Heritage|date=19 January 2017|publisher=Pen and Sword|isbn=978-1-4738-3376-0|location=|ref=harv|language=en}}\n*{{cite book |title = International Governmental Organizations |last = Peaslee |first = Amos Jenkins |publisher = Martinus Nijhoff |year = 1974 |isbn = 978-90-247-1601-2 |edition = 3rd |volume = 2 |location = London |ref = harv }}\n* {{Cite book |url = https://books.google.com/?id=pN5sJFKherYC&pg=PA113&dq=fabian+ware+%22Morning+Post%22#v=onepage |title = News and the British World: The Emergence of an Imperial Press System, 1876\u20131922 |last = Potter |first = Simon James |date = 2003 |publisher = Clarendon |isbn = 9780199265121 |location = Oxford |pages =  |language = en |ref = harv }}\n*{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/carrollquigley_angloamericanestablishment|title=The Anglo-American Establishment|last=Quigley|first=Carroll|publisher=Books in Focus|year=1981|isbn=|location=|pages=[https://archive.org/details/carrollquigley_angloamericanestablishment/page/n173 159]|author-link=Carroll Quigley|access-date=26 July 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825171210/https://archive.org/details/carrollquigley_angloamericanestablishment|archive-date=25 August 2019|url-status=live|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofnati19411950lees|chapter=Ware, Sir Fabian Arthur Goulstone|pages=[https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofnati19411950lees/page/926 926]-927|title=The dictionary of national biography : founded in 1882 by George Smith|editor-last1=Lee|editor-first1=Sidney|editor-last2=Nicholls|editor-first2=C. S.|editor-last3=Stephen|editor-first3=Leslie|last=Sillar|first=F.C.|date=1959|publisher=Oxford University Press|others=Internet Archive|isbn=|location=|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=fYI27dbGdX4C&pg=PA72&dq=%22Fabian+Ware%22#v=onepage&q=%22Fabian%20Ware%22&f=false|title=The Memorial to the Missing of the Somme|last=Stamp|first=Gavin|date=6 August 2010|publisher=Profile Books|isbn=978-1847650603|language=en|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book |title = Remembered: The History of the Commonwealth War Graves Commission |last = Summers |first = Julie |publisher = Merrell |year = 2007 |isbn = 978-1-85894-374-9 |location = London |ref = harv }}\n* {{Cite book|last=|first=|url=https://books.google.com/?id=1IZQAAAAYAAJ&q=%22the+sole+intermediary+between+the+british+army+in+the+field%22+%22all+matters+relating+to+graves%22&dq=%22the+sole+intermediary+between+the+british+army+in+the+field%22+%22all+matters+relating+to+graves%22|title=War Graves of the Empire|date=1929|publisher=Times Publishing Company|isbn=|location=|ref={{harvid|War Graves|1929}}|language=en}}\n*{{cite book |last1 = Ware |fi